history.content: We're trying to finalize registration over the next two weeks, and then should have an update. At this stage, it looks like students may receive 1 or 2 additional tickets, but that's completely contingent on current registration being complete. If we have 200 more students register after our final call then this would no longer be the case. Encourage your friends to register if they haven't! This is always difficult because there are inevitably some latecomers who missed our (many) announcements, and we'd like everyone to participate (if they wish to).

Hi, 

Can we get an update for the waitlist for getting more than 4 CS commencement tickets? I have some family members planning to travel to Berkeley and are anxious to hear an update. 

Also, if there are any graduating seniors who have extra tickets please let me know! I'd be willing to buy them from you :)
history.subject: Update for CS Commencement Tickets?
